  m_Text: "You can wait for the vault to open or unlock it instantly with dynamites.\n\nEach vault contains three out of the following seven types of item: gold bars, dynamites, diamonds and four different silver coins for upgrading your characters.\n\nFor more information on the probability of getting each reward visit <color=\"#1499bf\">our website</color>."
